            <h3>Finance and Financials</h3>
            <p>
                Let's face it, financials are not for everyone. Some people just don't like the tedious nature of
                tracking financials. But in business, financials and understanding thereof makes the difference between
                profitability($$) and a money pit or the worst case...bankruptcy. Many small business owners can tell you their revenue and whether
                they are able to make payroll and keep the machines going. But do they understand their cost structure? Know their break-even point?
                and how much they have to sell to make a profit.
                <hr />
                <figure>
