                </figure>
                <hr />
                Do you make/keep financial statements. A Balance Sheet, Income Statements and Cash Flow? You should always have these on hand. For financing, credit appraisal
                or when and if you decide to sell your business.
            </p>
            <p>
                Not everone can afford a full time accountant and an accountant is probably not going to help you determine your unit costs per product. Or how to allocate
