            <h3>Marketing and Operations</h3>
            <p>Financials are required to track the profitabilty of your business, but marketing and operations are essential to increase revenue
            and streamline costs to increase net profits. </p>
            <hr />
            <figure>
                <img class="figure img-fluid" src="~/Images/BusinessAreasOfFocus.jpg"style="max-height:50%;max-width:50%" alt="AreasOfFocus" />
