            </figure>
            <hr />
            <h4>Operations</h4>
            <p>
                Is your business job-focused or process-focused? In other words do you have a client come in and say "Build this widget for me
                and I will pay $200." Or, do you make 100 widgets and sell them to x number of customers for y$/widget. How do you minimize "cost-of-sales" while
                maximizing profit-margin. We can help you look through your work-flow for inefficiencies and target practices
                that are eating into your margin.
            </p>
            <h4>Marketing</h4>
            <p>Do you have a strategy for gaining visibility with your customers? Have you targeted a given segment to focus on? Do you know who your competitors
            are and how much share they command in the market? These are some of the questions that you should ask before you embark on a venture. If you 
            have revenue projections, this type of marketing analysis underpins those projections. We can help you perform a market analysis. With information
            in hand, you will have much more confidence in your projections going forward.
            </p>
            <p>If you are launching new product, perhaps you need to commission a <b>conjoint analysis</b> to determine what features and attributes are
            valued by your target market segment. We can help you launch a study and analyze the results to ensure your product will meet the needs
            of the marketplace.  Again, this type of study underpins your revenue projections and lends credibility to these numbers.</p>
            <p>Let TekEngine help you understand the full picture before you launch or at least navigate the choppy seas of today's market. </p>

